title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 §§ 151-2.3 - Effective date

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 §§ 151-2.3 - Effective date

State Regulations

This Subpart shall apply to all new deposits made into the ATF on or after July 1, 2007, for accidents occurring on or after January 1, 2001, as mandated by chapter 6 of the Laws of 2007. Notes
